{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 90489, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 15188, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有趣，cz宁波人，感觉能与上海人无障碍沟通", "timestamp": 1593961668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 90498, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 15188, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "上海话就是以苏州话，宁波话为底子，融合了其他苏南浙北吴语以及部分苏北江淮官话，形成的啊。", "timestamp": 1593961780, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 90500, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 15188, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般是同音字代替吧，不过学校会在脑海里自动翻译成学堂哈哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1593961792, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 90507, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 15188, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 很多普通话书面语词语上海话根本不会这么说，比如我也不知道硬读【零钱】怎么读，一般都读【零碎铜钿】。", "timestamp": 1593961993, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 90526, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 15188, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 对的，特殊词汇不翻译直接念太奇怪了，尤其是新出的名词，都要自动切换成普通话再切回去。零钱大概可以念lin dzi？2333", "timestamp": 1593962342, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 90537, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 15188, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "233cz对吴方言倍感亲切", "timestamp": 1593962560, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 90550, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 15188, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz宁波人 从小家人说普通话 现在cz只听得懂方言 但不怎么会说", "timestamp": 1593962713, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 90819, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 15188, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "宁波人开心报道！！！去上海就 没障碍 甚至听得懂大妈插队骂人的话...", "timestamp": 1593965410, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 91376, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 15188, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哇哦 同上海人顶顶", "timestamp": 1593994647, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 5, "pid": 15188, "reply": 9, "tag": null, "text": "#15181\n这个问题好。老早上海言话是可以直接读书面语写的书籍报纸的（照着字面一字不修改的读），但是现在小年轻连日常用语都讲伐来。\n霍格沃兹魔法学校直接读是hoq kaq oq tzy mu faq yaq yo\n翻译成上海言话再读就是hoq kaq oq tzy mu faq roq daon", "timestamp": 1593961211, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782588, "url": "", "vote": {}}}